from.S: base.calibration_maintenance cm INNER JOIN crosscheck.calibrations c ON cm.new_calibration_id = c.calibration_id INNER JOIN crosscheck.games g ON c.game_id = g.game_id

select.S: cm.calibration_maintenance_id, cm.date_created, g.game_id, cm.triggered_by, cm.tilt, cm.roll, cm.pan, cm.home_pixel_x, cm.home_pixel_y, cm.home_pixel_confidence, cm.radar_image_id, cm.new_calibration_id, cm.current_calibration_id, cm.baseline_calibration_id, cm.strike_zone_change_y, cm.strike_zone_change_y - LAG(cm.strike_zone_change_y, 1) OVER (PARTITION BY g.game_id ORDER BY cm.date_created) AS strike_zone_change_y_delta, cm.strike_zone_change_x, cm.strike_zone_change_x - LAG(cm.strike_zone_change_x, 1) OVER (PARTITION BY g.game_id ORDER BY cm.date_created) AS strike_zone_change_x_delta, cm.home_pixel_edge_score, cm.home_pixel_edge_score_absolute, getdate() as date_processed
